{
  "stem": "311.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On top of it, there was at least 20,000 Hasidim, which were not registered.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that-- they couldn't-- you could-- you can sleep in my house but you have to register.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It mostly was apartment houses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When somebody came over to sleep, even your relative or somebody, you had to register him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And next day, it was in the-- in the books, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not police station, in the book.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had to register in the station.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Whatever.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Each house had a book, you know, apartment house had a book.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somebody came in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I say, OK, he's going to stay over one night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So all right, so he-- But if he stood up-- let's say, my uncle came from Trzebinia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He had to stay for a week.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had to go to court or someplace else.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he registered and everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then when you left out, you know, you had to register out from that he was that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the Hasidim, they didn't have to register, since they were sleeping on the benches.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the-- in the shul.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were 500 shuls, you know, in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of them 400, 500 years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, the Alta Shul.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Old Shul, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And well, there was--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Old Shul?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Must be like, 450, 400.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know, anyway, it was built on a flat land.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was sinking all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now, when we-- even when we were kids, they explained to us why there was like a all around, like a little park.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then you had to go down steps, like eight, 10 steps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a museum now, I hear, the Old Shul.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Remuh?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Remuh Shul is a little [NON-ENGLISH] It's small.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
